bonfyre-tag — instant topic/intent tagging (fastText, pure C)

Usage:
  bonfyre-tag predict <model.bin> <text-file> [output-dir] [--top N]
  bonfyre-tag batch <model.bin> <dir> [output-dir]
  bonfyre-tag train <training-data> <model-out>
  bonfyre-tag detect-lang <text-file> [output-dir]
  bonfyre-tag status
